synopsis (EN)	Another Code R is a graphic adventure game. It is the sequel to Another Code: Two Memories

Set two years after the events of the previous game, a now 16-year-old Ashley is invited by her father to visit the camp ground of Juliet Lake. As the story progresses, Ashley attempts to find the truth about her mother's death.
